# Intito MasterFlow impact analysis for security
# Purpose: Evaluate security object dependencies affected by a version diff.
# Sources:
# - IMF.C.Diff
# - Security model objects referencing the managed dimension
# - IMF.C.Impact
# Parameters:
# - pPrefix: Naming prefix for Intito MasterFlow control objects. Default 'IMF'.
# - pDimensionCode: Managed dimension code.
# - pVersionId: Existing work version.
# Prolog:
# - Resolve diff scope for the selected version.
# Metadata:
# - Identify security artefacts depending on the dimension structure.
# Data:
# - Classify security impact caused by deletes, moves, or renamed keys.
# Epilog:
# - Write security-domain findings to IMF.C.Impact.

sPrefix = Trim(pPrefix);
If(sPrefix @= '');
  sPrefix = 'IMF';
EndIf;

